	   <tr><td colspan=2>You can use root to seperate two mobs that spawn near each other.  Cast root on one of the mobs.  If the other one dose not attack, move back a good distance.  When root wears off only the mob you cast on should come after you.  <br><br>Yodan<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
