	   <tr><td colspan=2>shaman do get blind spell that helps greatly if you wish to solo. (it won't work with pet tho) root & dot the mob & if root is broke, cast a quick blind then reroot the mob. I use to solo the Grif in EC this way at lvl 40s.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
