	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes that can work but try can get a Monk partner to help and you two will be able to take them easy.  Make sure you have your pet and buff up the monk, pet and yourself.  Debuff both of them and let the monk take one while you and your pet take the other.  Make sure you heal when needed and dot the hell out of them.<br><br>Glodor Dimwit<br>&nbsp;<br>Patience is a Virture, and something i don't have</td></tr>
