vel 5 corpses decay and are gone forever. This just goes to show you... always be polite and dont demand thngs from people 1) you dont know and 2) you are trying to get them to do somethin nice for you and finally 3) always thank the person and give that person a chance to say somethin before you go rushing off.<br>His own idiocy cost him a Knuckle Duster and some other very expensive monk gear. I think he must have either bought that stuff from E bay or gotten it from a RL friend or else he woulda known about the scale of wolf and spirit pouch. Oh well he got what he deserved, but its still funny =)<br> <br>If you liked this story rate it appropiatly please i love input.<br><br>Nitsujlak Barshemguud Ogre shammy of war<br>Prexus Server <br>Legacy<br>"Cowards die many times before their death"<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
